@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
@*<h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>*@
<div class="container">
    <div class="row text-center">
        <font back color="00000"></font>
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 sub-head">
            <h2 data-wow-delay="0.05s" class="wow rollIn animated"><font back color="0033cc"><strong>See it? Do it!</strong></font></h2>
            <p> GoodQRma is a first-of-its-kind service that provides everyone with everything needed to locate volunteer opportunities with using QR codes. We help volunteers and organizations to make the best match possible by using organic and dynamic crowd sourcing. GoodQRma provides fast, free, and an efficient way to connect volunteers with events. GoodQRma is an excellent source to help! Just create a profile, list your event, and print your event poster. It's as easy as 1,2,3.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row ">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
            <div class="media wow rotateIn animated" data-wow-delay="0.05s">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    <i class="fa fa-recycle fa-4x  "></i>
                </div>
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h3 class="media-heading"><font back color="0033cc">Our Community</font></h3>
                    <p>
                        How about a place where students and businesses could quickly organize their own people and even casual passerby traffic to clean up a section of their neighborhood? Place the tag where you'd like the magic to happen and let GoodQRma spread the word for you!
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="media wow rotateIn animated" data-wow-delay="0.05s">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    <i class="fa fa-history fa-4x  "></i>
                </div>
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h3><font back color="0033cc">Food Bank</font></h3>
                    <p>
                        America throws away almost 50% of their food, around $165 billion annually. GoodQRma works with volunteers who can come to pick up any unwanted, unopened and non-perishable food items from those who want to contribute and deliver it to their local food banks.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-3 wow bounceInDown animated" style="padding: 10px;" data-wow-delay="0.05s">
            <div id="carousel-slider" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn2.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQdqVuuSmxY-u41AORIBQA2pDjM0r6H-efbtTG3p7GgdVQDvWmkhA"style="height:275px">
                    </div>

                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="http://dru-cdn.zipcar.com/sites/default/files/styles/content-portal-slideshow-slide/public/2_fi_GiveGab.jpg?itok=MB2wbXlT" class="img-thumbnail" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src=" http://www.homesinjacksonvillefl.com/img/volunteers.jpg">
                    </div>
                    <div class="item active">
                        <img src="http://www.navy.mil/local/css/images/hi-res/131219-N-UX143-001.jpg">

                    </div>
                </div>

                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="0" class=""></li>
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="1" class=""></li>
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="2" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="2" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carousel-slider" data-slide-to="2" class="active"></li>

                </ol>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">

            <div class="media wow rotateIn animated" data-wow-delay="0.05s">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    <i class="fa fa-star-o fa-4x  "></i>
                </div>
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h3><font back color="0033cc">Homeless</font></h3>
                    <p>
                        Know an area where the homeless or displaced congregate? Use GoodQRma to organize others who would love to donate time or resources to feed and clothe the less fortunate. We could all use a some GoodQRma right?
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="Donate head-text stuff" data-wow-delay="0.05s">
                <div class="pull-left">
                    <i class="fa fa-life-ring fa-4x  "></i>
                </div>
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h3><font back color="0033cc">Organization</font></h3>
                    <p>
                        If physically going somewhere as a team is out of the question, volunteering as a team is still possible – If you’re willing to get creative. You could split your employees into teams and work for an event.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
<hr />
